list.name: Default
list.comment: * Project structure reorganized * flow and om packages are being externalized for a better modular design. Will be added on second release. * Added Virtual file system lib for speeding up scan process and avoid not needed IO operations on HDD. This lib is still an alpha version that needs to be optimized for high performance using Java NIO, concurrency support, etc.

* Modularized core dependencies in different packages for easier maintenance. * Added a new report template. * Changed graph node generation method
